    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_002121_0001" n="0001"/><!-- Change both @facs and @n -->
<lb/><opener><dateline rend="right"><add place="above">Acc 7237</add><hi resp="#U2"><placeName>Newstead Abbey,<add place="above">149</add>
<lb/>Mansfield, Notts.</placeName></hi>
<lb/><date when="1864-11-24">24 Nov <hi rend="underline">r</hi> 1857</date></dateline><!-- Change line info as appropriate -->
<lb/>    
<lb/><salute>My Dear Sir</salute></opener><!-- Change line info as appropriate -->

<lb/><p>I thank you
<lb/>very much for
<lb/>your kind invitation
<lb/>to dinner on Monday
<lb/>but I am still 
<lb/>busy at my work
<lb/>here and sorry
<lb/>that it does not
<lb/>permit my going
<lb/>South - I also

	<pb facs="liv_002121_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>thank you for 
<lb/>kindly writing on
<lb/>behalf of my son
<lb/>to <persName>D<hi rend="underline">r</hi> Sherman</persName> -
<lb/>your friend adopts
<lb/>the line we sometimes 
<lb/>had a smile over
<lb/>in <placeName><country>Africa</country></placeName> - several
<lb/>friends would write
<lb/>so many <add place="inline">other</add> friends 
<lb/>must have given 
<lb/>you the <unclear cert="medium">news</unclear> that
<lb/>I need not go into
<lb/>particulars - Or 
<lb/>I would have sent

	<pb facs="liv_002121_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>you the new book <add place="above">150</add>
<lb/>but feel certain that
<lb/>some other of your
<lb/>numerous friends have sent
<lb/>it - the upshot
<lb/>was we neither
<lb/>got the news nor
<lb/>the book - <unclear cert="low">too <!--no guess--></unclear>
<lb/>I thank you for 
<lb/>so far as you were
<lb/>concerned doing
<lb/>what you could</p>
<lb/><closer><salute>and am &amp;</salute><!-- Change as appropriate -->
<lb/><signed><persName>David Livingstone</persName></signed></closer><!-- Change as appropriate --> 

	<pb facs="liv_002121_0004" n="0004"/> <!--not sure this page belongs-->
<lb/><postscript><p>You asked in one
<lb/>of your notes what
<lb/>took another son
<lb/>into the <orgName>Federal Army</orgName>
<lb/>He says he was 
<lb/>kidnapped - and 
<lb/>he's refraining from 
<lb/>taking life even in 
<lb/>the frenzy of a 
<lb/>large <unclear cert="low"><!--no guess--></unclear> that
<lb/>he is there against
<lb/>his will - <persName>M<hi rend="underline">r</hi> Adams</persName>
<lb/>was here to lunch one
<lb/>day &amp; I had a promise
<lb/>that he would do what 
<lb/>he could - this makes
<lb/>me anxious for his brother</p></postscript>

            </div>
